"title": "6130: corruption",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6130",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of spiritual decay and moral dishonesty, arising from the effects of sin, which expresses itself in disobedience towards God.</p>\n<h2>Corruption of nature as a result of the fall</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:11\">GEN 6:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Sinful humanity is corrupt</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:4\">ISA 1:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40\">ACT 2:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:20\">DEU 32:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:16\">JOB 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1-Ps14:3\">PSA 14:1–14:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:1-Ps53:3\">PSA 53:1–53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:24\">PRO 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:12\">PRO 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:9\">HOS 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:15\">PHP 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:15-Titus1:16\">TIT 1:15–1:16</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel breaks the power of corruption</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1-2Cor7:2\">2CO 7:1–7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:20\">2PE 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:23\">JUD 1:23</a></p>\n<h2>Examples and causes of corruption</h2>\n<h3>Corruption as injustice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:23\">PSA 55:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:7\">2CH 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:16\">JOB 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:6\">ISA 58:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:9\">EZK 9:9</a></p>\n<h3>Disobedience towards God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:29\">DEU 31:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:5\">DEU 32:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:19\">JDG 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Denying the truth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:5\">1TI 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>Paganism</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:11\">EZR 9:11</a></p>\n<h3>Mocking justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:28\">PRO 19:28</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Taking bribes</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:7\">ECC 7:7</a></p>\n<h3>Bad company</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:33\">1CO 15:33</a></p>\n<h3>Careless talk</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:5-Jas3:6\">JAS 3:5–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:24\">PRO 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:12\">PRO 6:12</a></p>",
